To use SSH to connect to the VM, click SSH to the right of the instance name.
                       ||
  This launches an SSH client directly from your browser. 

  Install an NGINX web server by the commends 

Update the OS: sudo apt-get update 
Install NGINX: sudo apt-get install -y nginx
Confirm that NGINX is running: ps auwx | grep nginx


To see the web page, return to the Cloud console and click the External IP link in the row for your machine, 
or add the External IP value to http://EXTERNAL_IP/ in a new browser window or tab
